tegory\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1068,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/10\/28\/all-jannah-but-refuse\/","url_meta":{"origin":786,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: All Muslims enter Paradise but those who refuse","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 28, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Everyone from my nation will enter Paradise but those who refuse.\" They said, \"O Messenger of Allah, who will refuse?\" The Prophet said, \"Whoever obeys me enters Paradise, and whoever disobeys me has refused.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3855,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/27\/love-surah-ikhlaas-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":786,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Love for Surat al-Ikhlas leads to Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I love this chapter, 'Say: He is Allah, the One,'\" (112:1). The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYour love for it will admit\u00a0you into Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 774 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u00a0Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadi